{{otheruses||Shrines enshrining {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|Sugawara no Michizane|12=draft|12=draft}}|Tenmangū}} '''Tenjinja''' (天神社) refers to various {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|12=draft|12=draft}}. The name is read as "Tenjinja" or "Amatsukamuyashiro."
== Tohoku Region == * {{ill|Tenjinja (Tome)|ja|天神社 (登米市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Tome, Miyagi|ja|登米市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Miyagi Prefecture.
== Kanto Region == * {{ill|Tenjinja (Shiroi)|ja|天神社 (白井市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Shiroi, Chiba|ja|白井市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. * Tenjinja (Isumi) - Located in Isumi, Chiba Prefecture, in Misaki Town, Choja. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Nishitokyo)|ja|天神社 (西東京市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nishitokyo|ja|西東京市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tokyo. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Mitaka)|ja|天神社 (三鷹市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Mitaka, Tokyo|ja|三鷹市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tokyo. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Shiki)|ja|天神社 (志木市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Shiki, Saitama|ja|志木市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Saitama Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kamisato)|ja|天神社 (上里町五明)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kamisato, Saitama. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Saitama-Chuo)|ja|天神社 (さいたま市中央区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Saitama City, Chuo Ward. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Saitama-Minamiku-Futonoya)|ja|天神社 (さいたま市見沼区風渡野)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Futonoya, Minamiku, Saitama City. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Saitama-Midoriku-Terayama)|ja|天神社 (さいたま市緑区寺山)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Terayama, Midoriku, Saitama City. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kuki-Kitahiroshima)|ja|天神社 (久喜市北広島)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kitahiroshima, Kuki City. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Hanyu-Kamikawasaki)|ja|天神社 (羽生市上川崎)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kamikawasaki, Hanyu City. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kazo-Hiranaga)|ja|天神社 (加須市平永)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Hiranaga, Kazo City. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Yokosuka)|ja|天神社 (横須賀市)|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|Kurihama Tenjinja|ja|久里浜天神社|12=draft|12=draft}}) - Located in {{ill|Yokosuka|ja|横須賀市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Kanagawa Prefecture.
== Chubu Region == * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kurobe)|ja|天神社 (黒部市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kurobe, Toyama|ja|黒部市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Toyama Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Fujikawaguchiko-Oarashi)|ja|天神社 (富士河口湖町大嵐)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Oarashi, {{ill|Fujikawaguchiko|ja|富士河口湖町|12=draft|12=draft}}, Yamanashi Prefecture. ⇒ {{ill|Oarashi Tenjinja|ja|大嵐天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Tenmantenjinja (Iida)|ja|天満天神社 (飯田市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Nakanomachi, {{ill|Iida, Nagano|ja|飯田市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nagano Prefecture. ⇒ {{ill|Fumon-in (Iida)|ja|普門院 (飯田市)|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Tenjinja (Nagoya)|ja|天神社 (名古屋市中区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Naka-ku, Nagoya|ja|中区 (名古屋市)|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. ⇒ {{ill|Sakura Tenjinja|ja|桜天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Tenjinja (Obu)|ja|天神社 (大府市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Nagasago, {{ill|Obu, Aichi|ja|大府市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. ⇒ {{ill|Nagasago Tenjinja|ja|長草天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Tenjinja (Toyokawa)|ja|天神社 (豊川市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Mikamicho, {{ill|Toyokawa, Aichi|ja|豊川市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Komaki)|ja|天神社 (小牧市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Shimazu, {{ill|Komaki|ja|小牧市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. ⇒ Tenmantenjinja * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kasukawa)|ja|天神社 (春日井市勝川町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Katsukawacho, {{ill|Kasugai|ja|春日井市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kiyosu)|ja|天神社 (清須市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kiyosu|ja|清須市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Mihama)|ja|天神社 (愛知県美浜町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Mihama, Aichi|ja|美浜町 (愛知県)|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. ⇒ {{ill|Kowa Tenjinja|ja|河和天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Kitano Tenjinja (Konan)|ja|北野天神社 (江南市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kitanocho, {{ill|Konan, Aichi|ja|江南市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * {{ill|Hokai Tenjinja|ja|宝海天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Homi Town, {{ill|Tahara, Aichi|ja|田原市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture. * {{ill|Yoshida Tenjinja|ja|吉田天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Hirokoji, {{ill|Toyohashi, Aichi|ja|豊橋市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Aichi Prefecture.
== Kinki Region == * {{ill|Tenjinja (Osaka-Fukushima)|ja|天神社 (大阪市福島区)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Fukushima-ku, Osaka|ja|福島区|12=draft|12=draft}}, Osaka Prefecture. * Tenjinja (Osaka Kita-ku) - Located in Kokubunji, Kita-ku, Osaka. ⇒ {{ill|Yodogawa Tenjinja|ja|淀川天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * Tenjinja (Osaka Higashisumiyoshi-ku) - Located in Kuwazu, Higashisumiyoshi-ku, Osaka. ⇒ {{ill|Kuwazu Tenjinja|ja|桑津天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * Tenjinja (Toyonaka) - Located in Kamishinden, {{ill|Toyonaka|ja|豊中市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Osaka Prefecture. ⇒ {{ill|Kamishinden Tenjinja|ja|上新田天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kawachinagano)|ja|天神社 (河内長野市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kawachinagano|ja|河内長野市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Osaka Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kadoma)|ja|天神社 (門真市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Tsukidecho, {{ill|Kadoma|ja|門真市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Osaka Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Kizugawa)|ja|天神社 (木津川市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Yamashiro, {{ill|Kizugawa|ja|木津川市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Kyoto Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Nara-Takabatake)|ja|天神社 (奈良市高畑町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Takabatakecho, {{ill|Nara|ja|奈良市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nara Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Yamatotakada)|ja|天神社 (大和高田市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Miwacho, {{ill|Yamatotakada|ja|大和高田市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nara Prefecture. * Tenjinja (Sakurai) - Located in Saimiyama, {{ill|Sakurai, Nara|ja|桜井市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Nara Prefecture. * Tenjinja - Located in Kawahara 4-chome, Kusatsu, Shiga Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Akashi)|ja|天神社 (明石市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Akashi|ja|明石市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Hyogo Prefecture.
== Shikoku Region == * {{ill|Tokushima Bizen Tenjinja|ja|徳島眉山天神社|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Bizencho|ja|眉山町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tokushima|ja|徳島市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tokushima Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Tokushima)|ja|天神社 (徳島市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kitamiya, Tokushima. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Tokushima-Iritacho)|ja|天神社 (徳島市入田町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Irita, Tokushima.
== Kyushu Region == * {{ill|Tenjinja (Itoshima)|ja|天神社 (糸島市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kamiaru, {{ill|Itoshima, Fukuoka|ja|糸島市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Fukuoka Prefecture.
